╚══════╝: You can now translate the holo scrolls using a pipe and the tr command in addition to the cat command! 

GAME HINT: Remeber to use the rest function to skip to the next day (winning the game requires being on DAY 5, skip time wisely)

***NEW COMMAND:
tr
	--> pipe to a cat command to replace letters in a file. Decryption key: !@#$%^&* aeioustr
		ex. cat $inventory/+scrollOne | tr \!\@\#\$\%\^\&\* aeioustr

